<h2>ULEZ and LEZ charges and discounts</h2>

<p>If your vehicle is affected by the ULEZ and you intend to use it in the zone, you need to pay the daily ULEZ charge of &pound;100 for larger vehicles such as lorries, buses and coaches and &pound;12.50 for smaller vehicles like cars, small vans and motorcycles.&nbsp;</p>

<p>There are also three&nbsp;LEZ charges,&nbsp;&pound;200 or &pound;300 for larger vehicles and &pound;100 for smaller ones.</p>

<p>If you believe that the details we hold for your vehicle are incorrect or insufficient to calculate the correct charge you can register the vehicle with us.</p>

<p>To <a href="/modes/driving/compliance-registration/before-you-start">register a vehicle with us</a> you will need to provide evidence that it meets the ULEZ and/or LEZ standards.&nbsp;</p>

<h3>Showman's discount</h3>

<p>If you own a specially constructed or modified vehicle used for a travelling show, it may be eligible for a discount on daily ULEZ and LEZ charges. Find out more and set up a&nbsp;London Road User Charging account before <a href="/modes/driving/compliance-registration/before-you-start">applying for the Showman's discount</a>.</p>
